div1.p:
Q.(To
Solomon Jewell
). This is the knife your wife gave to you? - A. Yes.

THOMAS FRANKLIN sworn. - I am foreman to Messrs. Bown and Clarkson: I was sent for; I went into the shop, and saw the iron lying down at the entrance of the shop, near the scales; the prisoner was close by it;
James King
told me what had happened, and the prisoner did not deny any thing that was alledged against him. The iron is here. (It is produced).

Mr. Watson. (To
George Jeremy
). Q. Are you able to say when you last saw these articles in the shop? - A. I cannot.
